-----------------------------------------------------

I released this approx 2/3 weeks ago but had some problems so decided to rework alot of the map rather than just do a quick fix, the change log is to big to note down.

the map has 80 spawn points, 40 each side, theres 2 secrets, 1 of which is fairly easy to find and thus dosnt give that much of an reward, the 2nd is much more rewarding but i would not expect people to find it or figure it out to easily.

also the previous version had HDR i didnt compile HDR this time round because it was not needed, and overall i decided it was best to preserve the fps.

enjoy.
